description: AiXin Life International, Inc., together with its subsidiaries markets and sells nutritional consumer products and supplements in China. It operates through three segments: Advertising and Products, Pharmacies, and Hotels. The company sells products through its pharmacies, sales offices, exhibition events, and person-to-person marketing, as well as online. In addition, it operates the Shangyan Hotel located in the Jinniu District, Chengdu City. AiXin Life International, Inc. was incorporated in 1987 and is based in Chengdu, China.
